def solution(stdin: str) -> str:
    n, pos, l, r = map(int, stdin.split())
    tabs = []
    for i in range(n):
        tabs.append(int(stdin[i]))
    tabs.sort()
    tabs = [tabs[i] for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] - pos for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] + pos for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] - l for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] + l for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] - r for i in range(n)]
    tabs = [tabs[i] + r for i in range(n)]
    return str(min(tabs))
